description: Information about a single version of a JSON schema.

organizationId.description: The Synapse issued numeric identifier for the organization.

organizationName.description: The name of the organization to which this schema belongs.

schemaId.description: The Synapse issued numeric identifier for the schema.

schemaName.description: The name of the this schema.

versionId.description: The Synapse issued numeric identifier for this version.

$id.description: The full '$id' of this schema version

semanticVersion.description: The semantic version label provided when this version was created.  Can be null if a semantic version was not provided when this version was created.

jsonSHA256Hex.description: The SHA-256 hexadecimal hash of the UTF-8 encoded JSON schema.

createdOn.description: The date this JSON schema version was created.
createdOn.title: Created On

createdBy.description: The ID of the user that created this JSON schema version.
createdBy.title: Created By
